    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. i'm trying to check the boards but the airport feels totally chaotic right now. there's so many delays and people running around everywhere it's hard to focus. what's the most efficient way to look for a new route so i don't waste time standing in these massive lines?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
